name: Second Face #2 (ellos).
description: Photo (3d virtual camera shooting), Tono C @toocabanelas. “Second Face # 2 (ellos)”, is an immersive series of digital art that reflects on our second (or first) digital identity: avatars, metahumans, transhumans. The series is based on portraits that combine ancient photographic and cinematographic techniques with video game programming, 3D scanning, AI and Deep Learning. This piece is inspired by the work of Keijiro Takahashi / UnityDxrTest.
